            <div class="timeline__body glass">
              <span class="timeline__year">Spring 2021</span>
              <h3 class="timeline__heading script">How we met</h3>
              <p>It began, as the best stories do, by accident — a mutual friend's rooftop dinner in Surry Hills. Emma laughed at one of James' terrible jokes, and James decided then and there he would spend a lifetime earning that laugh.</p>
            </div>
