            </div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion__item reveal" data-reveal>
            <button class="accordion__trigger" aria-expanded="false">
              <span>What is the dress code?</span>
              <span class="accordion__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="accordion__panel"><div class="accordion__inner">
              <p>Formal attire, black tie optional. We'd be delighted to see soft champagne, blush and ivory tones. The ceremony is on grass, so consider block heels.</p>
            </div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion__item reveal" data-reveal>
            <button class="accordion__trigger" aria-expanded="false">
              <span>Do you have a gift registry?</span>
              <span class="accordion__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="accordion__panel"><div class="accordion__inner">
              <p>Your presence is the only present we need. Should you wish to give something, a contribution to our honeymoon adventure would be warmly appreciated — details are inside your invitation.</p>
            </div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion__item reveal" data-reveal>
            <button class="accordion__trigger" aria-expanded="false">
              <span>What happens if it rains?</span>
              <span class="accordion__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="accordion__panel"><div class="accordion__inner">
              <p>The Grand Estate has a beautiful covered pavilion on standby. Rain or shine, the day will be just as magical — no umbrellas required.</p>
            </div></div>
          </div>
        </div>
